title: Sorority Boys (2002)
description:
Sorority Boys (2002)


Director: Wallace Wolodarsky
Writers:Joe Jarvis & Greg Coolidge
Release Date: 22 March 2002 (USA)
Genre: Comedy
Tagline: Look Closer (Not That Close)

Plot Outline: After three rowdy guys get booted from their frat house, they dress up as women and pledge the \"ugly girl\" sorority, where they figure they\&#039;ll blend right in. In their new environment, the men relinquish their frat mentality and realize how hurtful they have been to women over the years. When their less-than-stunning female forms earn them an invite to a \"dog catcher\" party at their old frat, they decide to brave the harassment so they can grab the rest of their belongings from the house and make a clean break.
